Exercise 17.1: Install and Use Bootstrap Icons with Social Media Icons in Footer
Step 1: Include Bootstrap Icons CDN in <head>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">

Step 2: Add social media icons in the footer
<footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-4">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="#" class="text-white me-3 fs-4">
      <i class="bi bi-facebook"></i>
    </a>
    <a href="#" class="text-white me-3 fs-4">
      <i class="bi bi-twitter"></i>
    </a>
    <a href="#" class="text-white me-3 fs-4">
      <i class="bi bi-instagram"></i>
    </a>
    <a href="#" class="text-white fs-4">
      <i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i>
    </a>
  </div>
</footer>
Exercise 17.2: Replace Text Buttons with Icon-only Buttons
<div class="container text-center my-4">
  <!-- Text Button -->
  <button class="btn btn-primary me-3">
    Submit
  </button>

  <!-- Icon-only Button -->
  <button class="btn btn-primary" aria-label="Submit">
    <i class="bi bi-check-lg"></i>
  </button>
</div>
